snippet.title: Golden Opportunity! DragonKnight: A new fun NFT game that may make millionaires!
snippet.description:
Going over the overall concept of Dragon Knight, a fresh NFT based game that currently requires a low investment,  allows players to build an effective business model based on their diverse play-to-earn structure.

For all of those looking for an early opportunity to get into an NFT game.
